nodes.text: Kuat of Kuat was the hereditary title given to the head of House Kuat and Kuat Drive Yards. The Kuat of Kuat heir also took on the role of Technician in his management of Kuat Drive Yards. Kuat of Kuat resisted efforts from Emperor Palpatine and others to seize control of Kuat Drive Yards, enforcing the promise of generations of Kuat of Kuat that Kuat Drive Yards was eternal.
